first install the fortify package

then install the bootstrap because bootstrap does not come with fortify package

then create fortify login and register in web.php or app service provider in boot option

use Laravel\Fortify\Fortify;

Fortify::loginview(function () {
   return view('login');
   });

Fortify::registerView(function () {
  return view('register');
    });


the copy and paste app.blade.php 
where its gives you the defalut laravel nav bar and login and register link and if you are login  then it will give you logout option


